OL,3,CAmbulance service hosts essential
OL,4,C'bleed training'
OL,6,Fhas hosted a 'stop the bleed' training
OL,7,Fsession to give people the skills and
OL,8,Fconfidence they need to save lives.
OL,10,FStaff at the service say bleeding is
OL,11,Fthe single most preventable cause of
OL,12,Fdeath - but there are simple
OL,13,Ftechniques that can help prevent
OL,14,Ffatalities.
OL,16,FThe training day, which was held at
OL,17,Fthe West Midlands Ambulance hub, was
OL,18,Ffree to sign up to and helped
OL,19,Fparticipants know what to do to help
OL,20,Fstem the flow of blood before
OL,21,Fparamedics arrive.
