OL,3,CAmbulance service hosts essential
OL,4,C'bleed training'
OL,6,FIt involves using bleed control kits -
OL,7,Fof which there are over 800 across the
OL,8,FWest Midlands - or improvising with
OL,9,Fitems they may have on them.
OL,11,FNathan Hudson from the service says:
OL,12,F"It can be anything really from road
OL,13,Ftraffic collisions, industrial
OL,14,Finjuries or even stabbings."
