OL,3,CAmbulance service hosts essential
OL,4,C'bleed training'
OL,6,F"When people are faced with that kind
OL,7,Fof situation sometimes they don't know
OL,8,Fwhat to do so today is really about
OL,9,Fhelping the general public to have a
OL,10,Flittle bit of knowledge, a little bit
OL,11,Fof confidence, to be able to deal with
OL,12,Fthose types of situations before the
OL,13,Fmedics arrive."
OL,15,FThe event is run in conjunction with
OL,16,FcitizenAID, a charity that's provided
OL,17,Fthe videos and teaching for the
OL,18,Fsessions.
