OL,3,CAmbulance service hosts essential
OL,4,C'bleed training'
OL,6,FTheir work is backed by the James
OL,7,FBrindley Foundation - set up in the
OL,8,Fname of James who was fatally stabbed
OL,9,Fin Aldridge in 2017 as he walked home,
OL,10,Fit says it's vital learning.
OL,12,FMark Brindley says it's not just
OL,13,Fimportant in the Midlands, but across
OL,14,Fthe whole county.
OL,16,F"Knife crime and traumatic events
OL,17,Fhappen across the country and
OL,18,Feverybody needs to know how to save a
OL,19,Flife - and that includes their own
OL,20,Flife."
